data.description: Discover this stunning condo in a prime location of Smokey Point directly next to a community park. This charming condo features three spacious bedrooms, 1.75 well-appointed bathrooms, a open living room connected to a modern kitchen with top-tier appliances, high vaulted ceilings, and a private fenced yard for outdoor gatherings and barbeques. Enjoy a two-car garage and extra parking in the driveway, this convenient location is in very close proximity to i-5, Costco, Target, Walmart, Casinos, dining, parks, trails, and within walking distance to an Amazon facility for work. Whether you seek a home or an investment opportunity, this condo is ready to fulfill your desires. Don't miss out on seeing this remarkable property in person.
